	    <h3 class="heading">About</h3>
	    <p> 
	    	This website was developed as part of a year-long Bachelor's Essay study in 
	    	Computer Science at the College of Charleston. 
	    </p>
	    <p>
	    	My name is Nora and I am a double major in Spanish and Computer Science, so
	    	I decided a fitting capstone for my undergraduate experience would be to 
	    	investigate the topic of machine translation as it combines both disciplines.
	    </p>
	    <p>
	    	I started from the ground up, with no real experience or prior study in this field,
	    	researching and experimenting and learning a lot.
	   	</p>
